  Garrett grins mysteriously. "Now you're thinking like an adventurer. That map shows the way to something important. What it is... well, you'll have to discover that yourself."
  (set: $questLog to $questLog + (a: "Follow the map marked with X in the forest"))
]
(else)[
  "You need 25 gold for that. Come back when you've earned more."
]

[[Browse his wares]]
[[Leave the General Shop]]

:: Buy Healing Potion (15 gp)
(if: $gold >= 15)[
  (set: $gold to $gold - 15)
  (set: $inventory to $inventory + (a: "Healing Potion"))
  "Wise purchase," Garrett says. "You never know when you'll need it."
]
(else)[
  "Need 15 gold for that one."
]

[[Browse his wares]]
[[Leave the General Shop]]

:: Buy Lantern (20 gp)
(if: $gold >= 20)[
  (set: $gold to $gold - 20)
  (set: $inventory to $inventory + (a: "Lantern"))
